f(x) = \sum_{k=1}^\infty \frac{\sin kx}{k^3} \tag1
\int_0^{\pi/2} f(x)\,dx = \sum_{k=1}^\infty \left(\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}{(2k)^4}+\frac{1}{k^4}\right)\tag{a}
 |f'(x)|\le \pi/8 \tag{b} 
\int_0^{\pi/2} f(x)\,dx = \sum_{k=1}^\infty \int_0^{\pi/2} \frac{\sin kx}{k^3} \,dx =\sum_{k=1}^\infty \left(\frac{\cos 0}{k^4}-\frac{\cos k\pi/2}{k^4}\right) \tag2
|f'|
|f'(x)|\le \pi^2/6
|\cos kx|\le 1
f(x)=\frac{1}{12}(x^3-3\pi x^2+2\pi^2 x), \quad 0<x<\pi
